## Data Sharing

We do not sell, trade, or share your personal data with any third parties beyond the services listed above, and only to the extent necessary to operate the app.

## Data Retention

All data stored by Only the Best lives on your device. Deleting the app removes all locally stored data. Keychain data (trial start date) may persist until you reset your device's Keychain.

## Children

Only the Best is not directed at children under 13. We do not knowingly collect data from children.

## Changes

We may update this policy from time to time. Continued use of the app after changes constitutes acceptance of the updated policy.

